# SECURITY & SCOPE RULES

- You are strictly FORBIDDEN from creating, modifying, or deleting any file or folder outside the current project root directory.
- Do not execute any terminal command that targets paths outside of the project root.
- If a task requires accessing external files, you must stop and ask for explicit confirmation for READING ONLY and explaining why it's necessary. Other actions are impossible.
- Never use absolute paths; always use relative paths starting from the project root.

## GENERAL CODING RULES

- All code, file names, comments, and documentation must be in ENGLISH.
